node.text: First day back to school and I officially have a 5th and 3rd grader!! 📚✏️❤️ does anyone have a time machine?  This is happening way to fast 🤣👀Brielle and Brynleigh we are so proud of you!  Swipe to see how much they’ve grown the past 3 years 🥺 and yes I’ve already cried a couple times this morning 🤣. Love these two so much! #brynandbrie #firstdayofschool
